strings.Value: "I feel the breath of the Great God. He is near. He is here!"
"You usually just talk rubbish, this time I'm inclined to agree — you look worse than ever."
"You are pale. You need medicine. Or a blessing."
"I just itch to yell, "Leave our friend alone, you graverot!" — But you're the one who keeps calling him, dwarf."
"You should rest, Harrim. You don't look well!"
"You ask for trouble all the time. Should you be surprised when it finally arrives?"
